## Detailed product specs
> Write a product spec in this format:
>
> - Summary
> - User Need/Problem
> - Business Metrics
> - Primary Research (User Interviews, User Testing)
> - Secondary Research (Competitor Analysis, Benchmarks, Surveys)
> - Features in the form of Jobs-to-be-done
> - Post Mortem
> {{your content here}}

